<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/building-digital-uk> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Building Digital UK (BDUK) is helping to bring fast and reliable broadband and mobile coverage to hard-to-reach places across the UK - transforming people’s lives and driving economic growth. BDUK is part of the Department for Science, Innovation and Technology ."@en .
